{"tid":2112632,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"終於食到譚仔五小辣","createTime":"2020-07-17T12:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T08:53:52.000Z","uid":54530,"like":4,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"66a307abb9ddf003dd375215018a79ba26c2fa01","tid":2112632,"uid":54530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:45:46.000Z","msg":"以前食開清湯 發覺譚都唔好食<br />\n班fd次次叫親我食我都係搵loan捐 寧願自己一個去買燒肉飯算數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後都冇點食過譚仔 淨係去食d唔辣既撈米線<br />\n話說岩岩放工想買四寶飯食 點知係條公路塞左成粒鐘 勁肚餓 咁岩見到間譚仔三哥雲南米線 大大個海報見到撈薯粉 作為撈米線既fans就緊係去試啦<br />\n一入到餐廳<br />\n「唔該要個撈薯粉」然後正想叫十小既時候 眼尾發現最小都五小辣 後面又有大量人排緊隊 咁冇計啦 頂硬上！<br />\n一翻到屋企我開著部冷氣先 再慢慢食我人生第一個五小辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一啖，唔算太勁 都仲頂到<br />\n食多幾啖，條脷麻左，冇左知覺<br />\n食到一半，嘴唇開始發麻 我杯凍奶茶已經飲曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再食多d，個嘴腫埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後一野倒埋落個口！<br />\n我成功了！我食到譚仔五小辣啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家準備噴埋d鼻涕就打比女神約佢食譚仔 再示範點食辣比佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多 抹汗抹眼淚噴埋d鼻涕先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df417ba7d4d99fb33c837ef6107cd68bfee64d7","tid":2112632,"uid":124841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:46:27.000Z","msg":"勁 我淨係食到10小辣"},{"pid":"70f00f0cd847ee1594da11d2e436f5cf5aa7574a","tid":2112632,"uid":78383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:46:39.000Z","msg":"cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c59e3a9d9bbc8ba2d7eefc4a5e6653e08ebd20","tid":2112632,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:46:40.000Z","msg":"食開大辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6338ba6e8da4ce9ef6efa106e61d8821ca51b7b","tid":2112632,"uid":68675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:48:51.000Z","msg":"唔好意思食開中辣以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185605ff7f99bf5679dd80e6e5bb9aa305f6697f","tid":2112632,"uid":243455,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"譚仔清湯食黎把撚咩 無味嘅<br />\n<br />\n次次聽到人叫清湯 個心都係到恥微緊佢<br />\n<br />\n利申：3小"},{"pid":"516ebae9da805cc6e7bfcd0845c7d05d7ae1d111","tid":2112632,"uid":78235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"有次同個fd食譚仔<br />\n佢話如果我食特辣佢就請我食<br />\n平時我最勁都係食小辣<br />\n見有人話請食飯我就接受挑戰<br />\n<br />\n個fd好似無話請野飲<br />\n所以我堅持唔叫野飲<br />\n但係阿姐眨我食得太痛苦 主動送左杯凍檸茶比我<br />\n<br />\n食左兩個鐘 卒之比我食曬<br />\n<br />\n然後連續兩日都屙 個屎忽窿熱辣辣左好耐"},{"pid":"8b0d47e37100bb9cf3ed52c30f6b406a8d6ad22b","tid":2112632,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:50:14.000Z","msg":"燃燒的屎眼"},{"pid":"895cbdc0e6de281f51dde5ee07bcac2182801961","tid":2112632,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:51:02.000Z","msg":"樓主好波<br />\n我食左三年十小<br />\n琴晚下定決心叫左九小<br />\n食到打佯先食得完<br />\n仲痾左成晚<br />\n今日連工都返唔到"},{"pid":"b6f1e9716f8b09cacfdee12499df05fd30eeb0af","tid":2112632,"uid":265739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:53:40.000Z","msg":"坦齋嗚笑辣"},{"pid":"1b646af1dee42f10023d6b73785552d704189070","tid":2112632,"uid":208516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"食開重慶二小Sor"},{"pid":"0a0eff5b5c462ef9edb842fe76d121af8f07f66a","tid":2112632,"uid":308450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:09:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98a940f7b5c68d61304bf3e113e00ef1fac71460","tid":2112632,"uid":231231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:10:52.000Z","msg":"5小？同清湯有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99429b91bac4be76c7e0463143d21d5c7a512260","tid":2112632,"uid":227851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:13:56.000Z","msg":"5小咩黎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c166529d57ee58b7ba2648b88964118fa1d9871","tid":2112632,"uid":245594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:15:25.000Z","msg":"未食過譚仔"},{"pid":"23dae6c77ea4550ca34678d2458b83cf9d5d003b","tid":2112632,"uid":327209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:16:27.000Z","msg":"我食開小辣<br />\n<br />\n有時中辣"},{"pid":"81632b11fc8d6a3b39f3b0334b2e4ea430da7204","tid":2112632,"uid":2403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:22:27.000Z","msg":"之前試食中辣，飲左兩啖湯就頂唔順拎隻碗分開d湯先食到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 3小"},{"pid":"567313ac5b2f58d34a71f0d15a99430b43b64db3","tid":2112632,"uid":54530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a0eff5b5c462ef9edb842fe76d121af8f07f66a","tid":2112632,"uid":308450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"185605ff7f99bf5679dd80e6e5bb9aa305f6697f","tid":2112632,"uid":243455,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"譚仔清湯食黎把撚咩 無味嘅<br />\n<br />\n次次聽到人叫清湯 個心都係到恥微緊佢<br />\n<br />\n利申：3小"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:09:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"真 清湯我不如係屋企自己煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ed2d7823aea9e4eeaefacdfa58ffffb1a7b316","tid":2112632,"uid":274722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:19:37.000Z","msg":"樓主超勁，傳聞全世界食到5小辣既得8000人左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da40f20a786fe803317842df173f432f504a6130","tid":2112632,"uid":240399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:23:31.000Z","msg":"撈薯粉個五小辣係辣過湯嘅五小辣架"},{"pid":"66df215c4fa71831ce9d6048b231baa65849e715","tid":2112632,"uid":54530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:24:50.000Z","msg":"食開清湯既巴絲唔洗灰心 終有一日你會食到譚仔既真味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家準備向3小進發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab031861681e1917ed375f88532f653e57fce7d","tid":2112632,"uid":54530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da40f20a786fe803317842df173f432f504a6130","tid":2112632,"uid":240399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:23:31.000Z","msg":"撈薯粉個五小辣係辣過湯嘅五小辣架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:28:24.000Z","msg":"咁食湯我可以食小辣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9a060583ce63c3632932bbc4af95e6e99b07da","tid":2112632,"uid":155815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"我練左一年先食到小辣<br />\n